    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育视频播放的状态流转图。核心是从内容分发节点Education_ContentCDN开始，视频初始状态应该是静止的Still。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Still"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Still作为初始状态。那Still应该能流转到哪些状态？学生数据库Education_StudentDB需要关联进来吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Still要连到Education_StudentDB，表示视频静止时可以从学生数据库获取播放记录。另外Still还要能进入播放中的Moving状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上Still到Moving的流转，以及Still到Education_StudentDB的连接。Moving状态需要能回到Still吗，比如暂停的情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Moving和Still要双向互通。还有一个关键场景：播放过程中如果网络异常，要进入Crash状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Still",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Moving到Crash的流转。Crash之后怎么处理？需要重连到CDN重新加载吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Crash",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Crash要回到Education_ContentCDN，形成完整的恢复闭环。这样整个状态机就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Crash",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下整体结构：从Education_ContentCDN进入Still，Still可去Education_StudentDB或Moving，Moving可回Still或去Crash，Crash最终回到Education_ContentCDN。这样对吗？",
